<div class="columns">
  <div class="column image is-offset-3 is-4">
    <p id="intro-message">Trade Space is a free online marketplace that uses <a href="https://maps.google.com/pluscodes/" target="_blank">Google Plus Codes</a> for location — a free, open system that gives every place on earth a short address, even where street names don't exist. Anyone can find and share any location accurately. Buying and selling online, now for everyone.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="column is-2">
    <img class="image" src="/assets/images/shopping-cart.jpg" alt="">
  </div>
</div>

<div class="columns">
  <div class="column is-offset-3 is-2">
