<div class="columns">
  <div class="column">
    <div id="safety-advice">
      <h3>Some Shopping Safety Advice</h3>
      <hr>
      <h4 class="safety-advice-heading">Buyers</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Try to meet in person.</li>
        <li>Check the item is real.</li>
        <li>Try to pay cash.</li>
        <li>Ask for paperwork — especially when buying a car, electronics, or anything of value.</li>
      </ul>
      <h4 class="safety-advice-heading">Sellers</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>If someone's paying cash, make sure you check the banknotes are real.</li>
        <li>If a buyer says they've sent too much and asks for money back, it's a scam.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
